Package: holyhull
Type: Package
Title: Wrap your points in a Hull Batman!
Version: 0.0.01
Author: Jim Coll
Maintainer: Jim Coll <jamesmcoll@gmail.com>
Description: A wrapper around several useful hull creation tools and utilities.  Before you use this junk please consider using it's constituant utilities whos authors deserve all of the credit here, including Yihui Xie's [alphahull package](https://yihui.org/en/2010/04/alphahull-an-r-package-for-alpha-convex-hull/) - [source](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/alphahull/alphahull.pdf)
 & [concaveman](https://github.com/mapbox/concaveman) - [source](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/concaveman/index.html) & [ST_ConvexHull](https://postgis.net/docs/ST_ConvexHull.html) via SF - [source](https://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/sf/index.html)
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
